<li class="comment even score5" id="comment-1425418">
<h2>

<a class="anchor" href="/sondages/quel-reveil-matin-utilisez-vous#comment-1425418" title="Lien direct vers ce commentaire">#</a>
 
<a class="title" href="/nodes/97083/comments/1425418">mpd + chaine hifi</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/openbar" rel="author">openbar</a> <time class="updated" datetime="2013-01-21T19:27:22+01:00"><span class="date">le 21/01/13</span> <span class="time">à 19:27</span></time>.
Évalué à&nbsp;<span class="score">
5
</span>.
</p>
<figure class="image"><img alt="" class="avatar" height="64" src="//img.linuxfr.org/avatars/647/050/000/avatar.jpg" width="64" /></figure>
<div class="content">
<p>J'ai fait un script python qui me réveille progressivement, en augmentant le volume tout doucement si je veux, si bien que parfois je rêve pendant un certain temps avec la musique dans le rêve, ce qui est agréable avec une musique bien douce; <br />
Voila le script en cadeau:</p>
<pre>
<code class="python"><span class="c">#!/usr/bin/python</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">time</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">sleep</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">os</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">system</span>
<span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">datetime</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">datetime</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">date</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">timedelta</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">time</span>

<span class="k">while</span> <span class="bp">True</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">reveil</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s">"15:42"</span>
    <span class="n">debutVolume</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">0</span>
    <span class="n">finVolume</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">100</span>
    <span class="n">dureeMontee</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="mi">80</span> <span class="c">#secondes</span>

<span class="c"># on attend</span>
    <span class="n">rap</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">reveil</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">split</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">":"</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">heure</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">time</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">rap</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]),</span><span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">rap</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]))</span>
    <span class="n">tnow</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">datetime</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">now</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">time</span><span class="p">()</span>

    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">heure</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">tnow</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">jour</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">date</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">today</span><span class="p">()</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">timedelta</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">jour</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">date</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">today</span><span class="p">()</span>

    <span class="n">diff</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">datetime</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">jour</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">year</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">jour</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">month</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">jour</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">day</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">heure</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">hour</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">heure</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">minute</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">datetime</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">now</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="n">dormons</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">diff</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">days</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="mi">24</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="mi">60</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="mi">60</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">diff</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">seconds</span>

    <span class="k">print</span> <span class="s">"on va dormir "</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">dormons</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">sleep</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">dormons</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="c"># on commence</span>

    <span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">s</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">command</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="n">system</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"mpc "</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">command</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="n">s</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"volume 0"</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">s</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"play"</span><span class="p">)</span>

    <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">xrange</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">dureeMontee</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="n">vol</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">debutVolume</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">*</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">finVolume</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="n">debutVolume</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="n">dureeMontee</span>
        <span class="n">s</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"volume "</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">vol</span><span class="p">))</span>
        <span class="n">sleep</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">s</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"volume "</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="nb">str</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">finVolume</span><span class="p">))</span>
</code>
</pre>
</div>
<footer class="actions">
</footer>

